JRA-24918 introduced Advanced Connection Test.

This test should replace the previous implementation available on the create directory page and should be a required step of creating new directory.

So instead of having a "test connection", a "save" button and a cancel link at the bottom of the page have a "save and test" button that saves the settings and drops the admin into the advanced connection test page that is currently accessible through the "test" link on the page that lists all the user directories. Ensuring that the connection configuration is thoroughly tested for problems during the configuration process.

